      "text": "芽衣ちゃんがオカピを見つけたのかと思って来たら\n{user}さんがいたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came here thinking Mei-chan found the okapi‚\nbut {user}-san was here instead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、状況の落差に頭が追い付いていないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ your brain can’t keep up with the sudden change in the situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
