      "text": "様子を見に来たんだけど、別荘の電気はついてるのに\n誰もいないから焦って探しに来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came to check on you all‚ but the lights were on in the vacation house‚\nbut no one was there‚ so I rushed out to look for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん\nなるほど、そういうことだったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem.\nI see‚ so that’s what it was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
