      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、芽衣が声を上げた時は\nついにオカピを発見したのかと思いましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ when Mei raised her voice‚\nI thought she had finally found the okapi.",
