    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "肩透かしと言えば肩透かし……ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to call it a letdown‚ it’s a letdown…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのせいでみんなに\n恥ずかしいところを見せちゃったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of you‚ everyone saw me\nmake a fool of myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　俺、知らないうちに何かやらかしたか？\nもしかして、ここに来るのが遅かった……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Did I do something without realizing it?\nDid I… come here too late…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 76.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この時間帯に別荘にいないなんてただ事じゃないと\n思って、これでもかなり慌てて探したんだぞ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it wasn’t a good sign that you all weren’t at the villa\nat this hour‚ so I rushed out to look for you‚ you know…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
