      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あはははは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　な、なんだ？　どうして笑ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Wh-what? Why are you laughing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないです。{user}さんが\nいつも通りで安心しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nothing. {user}-san is\nacting like your usual self‚ so I’m relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか？　それならいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is that so? That’s good to hear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_03_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざ探しに来てくれてありがとうございます\n練習を見に来てくれたのも……嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for coming all this way to find us.\nAnd… I’m glad you came to watch our practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
